## Key Design Decisions

| Decision | Choice | Rationale |
|----------|--------|-----------|
| Database | MongoDB | Flexible schema, fast reads for redirects |
| Auth | JWT | Stateless, scalable |
| QR Library | `qrcode` npm | Mature, supports PNG/SVG |
| Frontend | React + Vite | Fast dev, modern tooling |
| Styling | Tailwind CSS | User requested, rapid UI development |
| Charts | Recharts | Lightweight, React-native |

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The redirect engine must be optimized for <200ms response time. 
> MongoDB indexes on `shortId` and `customAlias` are critical.
